00:40:41.330 --> 00:40:41.930 align:middle line:90%
>>ESTEP: Yeah.

00:40:41.930 --> 00:40:42.850 align:middle line:90%
Dennis Rader, I believe.

00:40:42.850 --> 00:40:43.140 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yeah.

00:40:43.140 --> 00:40:44.210 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:40:44.210 --> 00:40:45.650 align:middle line:84%
>>ESTEP: Well known
in his church.

00:40:45.650 --> 00:40:48.163 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Family would
have no idea he did this.

00:40:48.163 --> 00:40:49.580 align:middle line:84%
>>ESTEP: It's
almost as if they're

00:40:49.580 --> 00:40:53.383 align:middle line:84%
