00:40:57.588 --> 00:40:58.880 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: But they don't see it?

00:40:58.880 --> 00:41:01.073 align:middle line:90%
The family doesn't see anything?

00:41:01.073 --> 00:41:03.740 align:middle line:10%
>>ESTEP: Well, you know, I mean,
